./src:
	MIMICA's source files.
		- AEROCHEM: sources related to aerosol processes and chemistry
		- INTEG: sources for numerical integration and advection
		- IO: sources for input/output as well as initialisation
		- MAIN: main source code and drivers
		- MICRO: microphysics sources
		- PHYS: physical packages including SGS mixing, radiation, surface fluxes and thermodynamics
		- PRESSURE: pressure solvers (diagnostic and prognostic)
		- TOOLS: other source codes and functions
		- TYPES: data types and data structures (including shared_data, defining all shared data used by MIMICA)
